This tool is used for programming and/or changing a Linkbot's Serial ID.

Requirements
============

* Python3
* PyLinkbot (See: http://wiki.linkbotlabs.com/wiki/Learning_Python_3_with_the_Linkbot/Installation_and_Setup)


Installation
============

run the script:

    python3 setup.py install

or, to install only for the current user,

    python3 setup.py install --user

(On Windows machines, you may need to replace 'python3' with 'python.exe')

Usage
=====

To start the utility, open a terminal console and type the command:

    linkbot-serialid-tool

